<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />The Lord gave the orders,</para>

<para style="q1">and those who announced them were a great army.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12-13" style="v" />Kings of armies flee, they flee,</para>

<para style="q1">and the women waiting at home divide the plunder:</para>

<para style="q1">doves covered with silver</para>

<para style="q1">with wings of yellow gold.</para>

<para style="q1">When some of you people stayed among the sheepfolds, why did you do this?</para>
